Long term research pays off big.  People like to get paid.  Yes, of
course a lot of companies miss bets by not funding enough projects or
not funding the correct projects.  But an enormous amount of valuable
research does come from companies.

The stock market has recognized this, and funds biotech companies at
enormous price/earnings ratios in order to finance their long term R&D
