What feature was it (if you remember)?  What was "Science's" explanation, or 
did they offer any?  The best images of the Crater Pyramid (one of the most 
striking crater-rim formations) is given a really good analysis in Mark 
Carlotto's "The Martian Enigmas," second edition.  I'm not aware of a 
