to assume that _every single one_ is going to employ a variation of the 
nanotech scenario that obviously sits well with members of this mailing list. 
 Some of them?  Quite probably.  But _all_ of them?  I can't make this leap 
without knowing more about the civilization/s under question...and at this 
point, unfortunately, we don't know anything at all.  We ourselves are a 
rather long way from the sort of nanotech you're describing, so we can't 
really even use _ourselves_ as an example.

