I tend to think so, but since we've no examples of such, this is all
speculation.  I also wonder if it would even be necessarilty to get
materials from planets at all.  My guess is that when you needed materials,
you can finds hunks of rock and ice or just gather some dust and gas -- if
recycling won't do the trick.

> If that is the case, why should they be in a hurry when
