acidophilus and bifidus - within yoghurt or their own - can help replace
friendly gut flora if they are depleted. If you have taken antibiotics or
yeast (bread, beer, vegemite) you might need some of these flora. Digestive
enzymes may also be helpful.
Gotta love that liver. Fruit fruit fruit seems to help. Also I have found St
Mary's Thistle and Dandelion root tea have helped me.
