~> Eugene Leitl <eugene.leitl@lrz.uni-muenchen.de> wrote:

> paul@i2.to writes:
> 
>  > I agree. Why waste the benefits of diversity and *unique* informational
>  > structures (us) in the sole pursuit of more raw materials for computronium?
