   Source:  Publishers Weekly, June 21, 1999 v246 i25 p61.
                                                                              
    Title:  CENTAURUS: The Best of Australian Science Fiction.(Review)
                                                                              
 Subjects:  Books - Reviews
   People:  Hartwell, David G.
